Prerequisites:
-------------
gnu c++ compiler - c++0x: >= 4.3, c++11: >= 4.7
standard template library (generally comes with c++ compiler)
boost library
numeric extension to boost library
openmpi library (> 1.4.4)
nvidia cuda (> 4.0)
parallel hdf5 library
libtiff library

prerequisites of hdf5:
libz
libsz
